status.full_text:
On the centenary of its protection as a National Park, Poland's Govt just signed a new plan to log more areas of Bialowieza Forest.

This is one of Europe's most precious sites. Campaigners will continue the struggle to safeguard the forest.

https://t.co/pqwxs8Qguo
